---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Why Choose Us?" description="Learn about the key benefits of New Leaf Academy's personalized tutoring services." />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Why Choose Us?</h1>
			<p>
				At New Leaf Academy, we believe that every student has the potential to succeed. We understand that a great tutor does more than just teach; they build confidence, inspire curiosity, and tailor their approach to each individual. Our commitment is to provide a supportive and effective learning environment that leads to lasting academic success.
			</p>
			<h2>Our Commitment to Your Success:</h2>
			<ul class="reasons-list">
				<li>
					<strong>Proven Results & Expert Tutors:</strong> We have a strong track record of helping students achieve top grades. Our specialist tutors are not only experts in their subjects but are also dedicated to helping you succeed.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Empathetic & Personalized Learning:</strong> We have extensive experience helping students with neurodivergence, SEND, dyslexia, dyscalculia, autism, and ADHD. Our tutors build genuine rapport and trust, ensuring every session is a supportive space where students feel understood and confident.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Flexible & Student-Led Sessions:</strong> Your schedule matters. We offer flexible class scheduling seven days a week to fit your life. Our sessions are led by the student, ensuring you get help on exactly what you need, when you need it.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Modern & Effective Teaching:</strong> We use a blend of fresh teaching methods, cutting-edge techniques, and the newest technology. Our tutors create engaging lessons and utilize the most effective online resources to provide the best possible education.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	:root {
		--primary-color: #2c4fb9;
		--text-color: #333;
		--font-family-body: sans-serif;
	}

	body {
		font-family: var(--font-family-body);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	main {
		color: var(--primary-color);
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
	}

	h1 {
		color: var(--primary-color) !important;
		font-size: 2.5em;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}

	p {
		color: var(--text-color);
		font-size: 1.1em;
	}

	h2 {
		color: var(--primary-color) !important;
		font-size: 1.8em;
		margin-top: 2em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}

	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
		line-height: 1.5;
		background-color: #f9f9f9;
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 10px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	li strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.2em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
		color: var(--primary-color);
	}

	/* Responsive Design with Media Queries */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		main {
			padding: 0 1em;
			margin: 1em auto;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2em;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.5em;
			margin-top: 1.5em;
		}

		p {
			font-size: 1em;
		}

		li {
			padding: 1em;
			margin-bottom: 1em;
		}

		li strong {
			font-size: 1.1em;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		main {
			padding: 0 0.5em;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 1.8em;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.3em;
		}

		li {
			padding: 0.8em;
		}
	}
</style>